OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,FWords by Producer Hannah Ward-Glenton
OL,7,FWhile the UK is experiencing record-
OL,8,Fbreaking temperatures, some people can
OL,9,Fsuffer more in the heat than others.
OL,11,FDr Anisha Patel, a GP specialising in
OL,12,Fwomen's health, says there are certain
OL,13,Fgroups of women for whom the hot
OL,14,Fweather can be particularly difficult.
OL,16,FITV News explains how women can be
OL,17,Fworse effected, and how to look after
OL,18,Fyourself when temperatures start to
OL,19,Fsoar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
