OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782350285
OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,FThe hormones oestrogen and
OL,6,Fprogesterone really affect how bodies
OL,7,Fregulate body temperature, and that's
OL,8,Fparticularly potent during your period.
OL,10,F"On your period, the second half of
OL,11,Fyour cycle, your body temperature is
OL,12,Fhigher, so you might feel hotter in
OL,13,Fthat period of time," Dr Patel said.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
