CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782350285
OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,FAnd hormones also come into play
OL,6,Fduring the menopause, when oestrogen
OL,7,Flevels decrease, causing hot flushes,
OL,8,Fnight sweats and poor sleep, which
OL,9,Fsubsequently make the heat seem even
OL,10,Fmore unbearable.
OL,12,F"Your temperature regulation system
OL,13,Fbasically becomes unstable with the
OL,14,Ffall in hormones, which can be really
OL,15,Foverwhelming for many women," Dr Patel
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FBeing pregnant comes with its own
OL,19,Fchallenges in the heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
