FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782350285
OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,F"Your metabolic rate, your heart rate,
OL,6,Fyour blood volume all increase and so
OL,7,Fyour body has to work harder to keep
OL,8,Fcool," Dr Patel said.
OL,10,FNational Childbirth Trust (NCT) says
OL,11,Fthat while pregnant women are usually
OL,12,Fable to adjust their body temperature,
OL,13,Fextreme heat does pose risks for both
OL,14,Fthe mother and the baby.
OL,16,FRisks can include dehydration, heat
OL,17,Fexhaustion and heat stroke.
OL,19,FYou can find more detailed advice
OL,20,Frelated to pregnancy and the hot
OL,21,Fweather on the NCT website.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
