CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782350285
OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,F"If your iron is low, for example, the
OL,6,Foxygen delivery is less efficient,
OL,7,Fyour heart's got to work harder and
OL,8,Fyou feel more fatigued, your exercise
OL,9,Ftolerance reduces and so that can also
OL,10,Fbe impacted as well," Dr Patel said.
OL,12,FShe also highlighted that it is not
OL,13,Fnecessarily all women who are worse
OL,14,Faffected by the heat, but specific
OL,15,Fgroups of women depending on their
OL,16,Findividual bodies.
OL,18,FWhat should you do when it's really
OL,19,Fhot?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
