OL,3,CWhy do women suffer more in the heat?
OL,5,FFor women who are likely to suffer
OL,6,Fmore in hot temperatures, the best
OL,7,Fthing to do is to try and prepare and
OL,8,Fprevent getting overheated or heat
OL,9,Fexhaustion.
OL,11,FDr Patel recommends the following tips:
OL,13,F"I think it's about just being aware
OL,14,Fthat we've just got to take a little
OL,15,Fbit of care of ourselves, particularly
OL,16,Fif we're these more vulnerable groups
OL,17,Fand in the heat," Dr Patel said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
